data.title: The Alphabet Killer
data.meta_description: Find out how to watch The Alphabet Killer. Stream The Alphabet Killer, watch trailers, see the cast, and more at TV Guide
data.text:
2007

1 hr 38 mins

Drama, Suspense

R

Watchlist

Chilling psychological thriller stars Eliza Dushku as a driven detective who has a nervous breakdown while investigating a serial-killer case and spends two years in institutionalization, only to return to find the murderer is still at large and that there have been more homicides with the same M.O. Cary Elwes, Timothy Hutton, Michael Ironside, Bill Moseley, Tom Malloy (who wrote the fact-based script about a series of murders in Rochester, N.Y., in the 1970s). Directed by Rob Schmidt.
